      "title": "Tamil National Alliance also to Dallas",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The party says that it has decided to give the support of the Tamil National Alliance to Parliamentarian Mr. Dallas Alahapperuma in the parliamentary vote to elect a new president.",
        "The vote to elect the new president is scheduled to be held tomorrow in Parliament."
